threads.title: A1466 820-00165-A no power
threads.message:
Hi,

I have an A1466 820-00165-A that has no power.

I have green light, no fan spin, and it only consumes 0.20A no bench PSU.

I  don't have PM_SLP_SUS_L, PM_SLP_S4_L, PP5V_S4 and PP3V3_S4 (0V).

Can you help?

threads.title: A1466 820-00165-A no power
threads.message:
Do you get 3V3_S5?
Check PM_BATLOW_L, SMC_ADAPTER_EN, PM_DSW_PWRGD, PCH_DSWVRMEN and the 4 PCH's RTC signals.
